<h3>GitHub上传模块的修改</h3>
<p>--------------------
<button id="copyButton" style="color: black;height: 30px;" >复制文字</button>
</p>
<div contenteditable="true">
<p>我尝试修改一个GitHub的上传模块，这个模块当中，它可以去兼容已有的文件的重新修改。</p>
</div>

<audio controls>
  <source src="https://whisper.solidunk.top/wspwk/20250328210134.m4a">
</audio>

<script>
  document.getElementById('copyButton').addEventListener('click', function() {
    const textArea = document.querySelector("div");
    const text = textArea.textContent;
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(text)
  });
</script>
